Business in China
In Dec 2011, E. Bon Group established its first flagship store along Shiliupu, Huangpu River, at the proximity of the Shanghai World Expo venue. The store, which occupies over 14,000 sq. ft. in a modern structure, is a 2-level high showroom displaying artpieces of designers. Originated in Europe, these quality products exhibit simplicity, modern and laid-back styles in this old city. 


