Description




E. Bon Holdings Limited is a Hong Kong-based investment holding company principally engaged in the wholesales of architectural hardware and household equipment. The Company operates through three segments. The Wholesale segment is engaged in the wholesales of architectural hardware, bathroom equipment, furniture, and kitchen equipment to contractors, property developers and dealers, as well as the provision of installation services of kitchen equipment and furniture. The Retail segment is engaged in the importing and sales of architectural hardware, bathroom equipment, furniture, and kitchen equipment through its retail outlets, as well as the provision of installation services of kitchen equipment. The Construction and Decoration segment is mainly engaged in construction and decoration businesses in China.







